Isaac Abraham, Director, Compositional IT
  &ldquo;Farmer quickly became an essential tool for Continuous Deployment at our F# projects. Clean DSL, great documentation, growing support of various Azure services and PR-friendly approach made Farmer to be one of the best open source projects in these days.&rdquo;
Roman Provazník, F# Lead Developer, CN Group
  &ldquo;Holy moly, this was a breeze!! I&rsquo;m SO going to use this more often, even if it&rsquo;s just to get a baseline for a customer. Saves tons of time!
Jan De Vries, Microsoft MVP
